cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper deals with deep neural networks for multi-modal sensor fusion, which involves computer vision (CV) and machine learning (ML) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely categories. The paper also proposes a new gating architecture, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with multi-modal sensor fusion, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM).
